PrecisEnactment of the DNA IDENTIFICATION REGULATIONS which prescribe the components of a DNA Data Bank Sample Kit and the circumstances in which DNA information shall be removed from the Data Bank, specify how a DNA profile is to be transmitted by electronic means and how personal information is to be protected when it is made available to other parties pursuant to an international agreement.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2000-0300 Publication Date: 2000-08-16
Attachments
precis:
Enactment of the DNA IDENTIFICATION REGULATIONS which prescribe the
components of a DNA Data Bank Sample Kit and the circumstances in which
DNA information shall be removed from the Data Bank, specify how a DNA
profile is to be transmitted by electronic means and how personal
information is to be protected when it is made available to other parties
pursuant to an international agreement.
